20,1,$1+$1,$4,$5,$6,$7,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$6,$7,$8,$9,0*
20,1,$1+$1,$8,$9,$2,$3,0*%
%AMRotRect*
0 Rectangle, with rotation*
0 The origin of the aperture is its center*
0 $1 length*
0 $2 width*
0 $3 Rotation angle, in degrees counterclockwise*
0 Add horizontal line*
21,1,$1,$2,0,0,$3*%
